  <brief_title>Phase II Study of AS1402 Combined With Letrozole to Treat Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomised, Open-Label, Multicentre Study of AS1402 in Combination With Letrozole as First Line Treatment in Postmenopausal Women With Locally Advanced or Metastatic Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
