  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the overall tumour response rate per RECIST in
      postmenopausal women with metastatic or locally advanced breast cancer receiving AS1402 in
      combination with letrozole compared to letrozole alone
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
